---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="B2B & B2G | PDAS 2026">

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 border-b border-slate-800 bg-[#020617] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.6) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.6) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 48px 48px;"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="relative w-2 h-2 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-sky-400 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-60"></span>
          <span class="relative w-2 h-2 bg-sky-400 rounded-full block"></span>
        </span>
        <p class="text-[11px] uppercase font-mono tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">SYS.DIR // Highlights // B2B & B2G</p>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-8">
        B2B &<br />
        <span class="text-transparent" style="-webkit-text-stroke: 1px white;">B2G</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-sky-400 pl-6">
        While the Expo floor showcases the 'what,' the PDAS B2B & B2G Marketplace defines the 'how.' A high-velocity, structured environment engineered to bypass traditional bureaucracy and create a fast-track for defence contracts, technology transfers, and strategic collaborations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- B2G SECTION -->
  <section class="py-24 border-b border-slate-800 bg-[#070d1e]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">

          <p class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">01 // Sovereign Interface</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-3 leading-tight">B2G: Direct Access to the<br />Architects of National Security</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">Business-to-Government Wing</p>

          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-12 border-l-2 border-sky-400 pl-6">
            The B2G wing is a dedicated interface for alignment between the state's strategic needs and the industry's manufacturing capabilities. It serves as a transparent conduit for the Ministry of Defence and the Armed Forces to communicate directly with the builders of the nation.
          </p>

          <!-- B2G Feature Cards -->
          <div class="space-y-4">

            <details class="group border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-slate-700 transition-colors">
              <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-white font-bold uppercase text-sm list-none">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <span class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest">B2G.01</span>
                  <span>The "Pathfinder" Briefings</span>
                </div>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-sky-400 flex-shrink-0 ml-4">
                  <svg fill="none" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-6 pb-6 border-t border-slate-800 mt-0 pt-4 text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed">
                > Exclusive, closed-room sessions where senior leadership from the Army, Navy, and Air Force outline their Technology Perspective and Capability Roadmap (TPCR).<br /><br />
                > For the first time, industries gain a 10-year outlook on the military's requirements, allowing for precise R&D investment alignment.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-slate-700 transition-colors">
              <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-white font-bold uppercase text-sm list-none">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <span class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest">B2G.02</span>
                  <span>The Indigenization Clinic</span>
                </div>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-sky-400 flex-shrink-0 ml-4">
                  <svg fill="none" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-6 pb-6 border-t border-slate-800 mt-0 pt-4 text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed">
                > One-on-one sessions with DRDO and Department of Defence Production (DDP) officials to navigate the New Defence Acquisition Procedure (DAP).<br /><br />
                > Gain clarity on "Make-I" and "Make-II" categories and understand how to qualify for government-funded prototyping programmes.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-slate-700 transition-colors">
              <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-white font-bold uppercase text-sm list-none">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <span class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest">B2G.03</span>
                  <span>User-Industry Interactivity</span>
                </div>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-sky-400 flex-shrink-0 ml-4">
                  <svg fill="none" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-6 pb-6 border-t border-slate-800 mt-0 pt-4 text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed">
                > A specialized forum where Armed Forces representatives present "Problem Statements" regarding spares, component aggregates, and substitution engineering.<br /><br />
                > Industries offer direct solutions for the immediate operational needs of the frontline.
              </div>
            </details>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar Status Panel -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <div class="sticky top-24 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg bg-[#020617] shadow-[0_0_60px_-15px_rgba(56,189,248,0.15)]">
            <div class="border-b border-slate-800 px-6 py-4">
              <p class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">> STATUS // B2G MODULE</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 space-y-4 font-mono text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">
                <span class="text-slate-500 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest">Pathfinder</span>
                <span class="text-green-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">● Active</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">
                <span class="text-slate-500 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest">Indigenization</span>
                <span class="text-green-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">● Active</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-3">
                <span class="text-slate-500 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest">User-Industry</span>
                <span class="text-green-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">● Active</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <span class="text-slate-500 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest">Access Level</span>
                <span class="text-sky-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">Registered</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-slate-800 p-6">
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed">
                > Policy meets the factory floor. The B2G Marketplace is the nervous system of the summit.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- B2B SECTION -->
  <section class="py-24 border-b border-slate-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">

      <p class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">02 // Global Matchmaking</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-3 leading-tight">B2B: Precision Networking<br />Powered by Intelligence</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-12">Business-to-Business Wing</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">

        <!-- Tier-1 to MSME Bridging -->
        <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-8 transition-all hover:border-sky-400/40">
          <p class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">B2B.01</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">Tier-1 to MSME Bridging</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Acting as the bridge between Global OEMs and the Peninsula's MSME powerhouse — connecting precision capability to global procurement demand.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm">
            <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-400/50 pl-4">
              <p class="text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 font-bold">Offset Fulfillment</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400">A dedicated corridor for foreign OEMs to identify reliable Indian partners to meet their offset obligations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-400/50 pl-4">
              <p class="text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 font-bold">Sub-System Integration</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400">SMEs specializing in precision machining, sensors, and advanced materials get private Pitch Minutes with Tier-1 integrators.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Investor Pit -->
        <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-8 transition-all hover:border-sky-400/40">
          <p class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">B2B.02</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">The Investor Pit</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The Defence sector is capital-intensive and requires visionary backing. We bring together Defence-focused capital with the Peninsula's brightest deep-tech startups.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm">
            <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-400/50 pl-4">
              <p class="text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 font-bold">Venture Capital for Deep-Tech</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Defence-focused VCs, Private Equity firms, and Angel Investors meet startups from the Peninsula's incubation hubs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-400/50 pl-4">
              <p class="text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 font-bold">Scaling Capital</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Focused on dual-use technologies, bridging the valley of death between prototype and mass-produced military asset.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- AI Matchmaking Callout -->
      <div class="border border-sky-400/30 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-[0_0_40px_-10px_rgba(56,189,248,0.15)]">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="relative w-3 h-3 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-sky-400 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-60"></span>
              <span class="relative w-3 h-3 bg-sky-400 rounded-full block"></span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">AI-Driven Matchmaking // ACTIVE</p>
            <p class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">We replace "random networking" with intelligence.</p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Our proprietary platform analyzes your company's capabilities and aligns them with the procurement needs of global giants — before you walk through the door.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STRATEGIC FOCUS: GLOBAL SUPPLY CHAIN -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-[#070d1e]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">

      <p class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">03 // Value Chain Advancement</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-3">Strategic Focus:</h2>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-12">The Global Supply Chain</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">

        <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg p-6 flex gap-6 hover:border-sky-400/40 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16">
            <span class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">SC.01</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-sm mb-2">Substitution Engineering</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">A dedicated desk for industries to explore the Positive Indigenisation Lists, identifying foreign-made components that can be re-engineered and manufactured locally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg p-6 flex gap-6 hover:border-sky-400/40 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16">
            <span class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">SC.02</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-sm mb-2">Certification & Standardization</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Direct interaction with CEMILAC and DGAQA ensures every partnership formed at PDAS is built on a foundation of international quality standards, making products export-ready from Day 1.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg p-6 flex gap-6 hover:border-sky-400/40 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16">
            <span class="text-sky-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">SC.03</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-sm mb-2">Consistent Product Support</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Building a life-cycle support model ensures Indian manufacturers can provide dependable spares and aggregates to both the Indian Armed Forces and international buyers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Bottom CTA -->
      <div class="mt-16 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/participating-options" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-[#008718] text-white px-8 py-4 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/30 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all flex items-center gap-3">
          Register to Exhibit
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="square"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/visitor-profile" class="border border-slate-700 text-white px-8 py-4 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold rounded-lg hover:border-slate-400 transition-all bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
          Register to Visit
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
